  <summary date="2018-03-26T20:28:00Z" status="Introduced in House">No Drilling in Our Backyards Act

This bill amends the Mineral Leasing Act to prohibit the Department of the Interior from issuing a permit for any oil and gas drilling operation that is located within 1,500 feet from a home, business, school, or other building that requires special protection.</summary>
